{"tid":2134724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓬佩奧算唔算係近代最有影響力既國務卿?","createTime":"2020-08-01T02:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T17:04:21.000Z","uid":88737,"like":71,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"392db0f410f825dca46474a3d5d29c917c0d0771","tid":2134724,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:48:58.000Z","msg":"早前發表左反共宣言(新杜魯門宣言),又積極拉攏盟友組成反共聯盟,呢D應該係總統TRUMP做既野黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過TRUMP太串,由TRUMP出馬好大機會搞禍成件事,其實之前TRUMP局棋行得無錯,只係一個武肺打亂晒,又放唔低身段,要放權比蓬佩奧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對比起前幾任國務卿,奧巴馬時期克里話支持係台灣行一國兩制,希拉莉個八婆話要賣台灣換果萬幾億美國國債<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧做到實事,強硬正氣得黎又有種平易近人既感覺,近代真係搵唔到邊個同佢有得比"},{"pid":"5acb799d9a5be21f16430ca4e4ba6c424f11097e","tid":2134724,"uid":155095,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:51:57.000Z","msg":"不過國務卿係由總統任命<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧任期得返唔夠半年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f5a57b4c799f6f2f6593921606dc4e12dff4a9","tid":2134724,"uid":186882,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:54:05.000Z","msg":"希拉里大d，賣國賣到支那咁撚肥"},{"pid":"9dcb491693c6540d4fd08067278230d1988e9395","tid":2134724,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:54:29.000Z","msg":"如果biden上任唔換人就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a70a4276e889f3e113c70e30d2b86cb8d940242","tid":2134724,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:55:31.000Z","msg":"已當左佢做未來總統"},{"pid":"08118a2e7e0ab8679ed175196b9b8cade35201b1","tid":2134724,"uid":288071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9dcb491693c6540d4fd08067278230d1988e9395","tid":2134724,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:54:29.000Z","msg":"如果biden上任唔換人就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:57:17.000Z","msg":"無可能，民主黨3千幾萬個黨員唔用要用敵黨嘅人？仲要係國務卿"},{"pid":